    "headline": "PTC lifts annual revenue forecast on steady software demand",
    "summary": "May 6 - PTC Inc on Wednesday raised its full-year revenue forecast, citing continued demand ‌from manufacturers using its software to digitize ‌their design and production processes. Shares of the Boston-based company rose ​nearly 4% in extended trading. PTC has benefited as manufacturing and industrial clients continue to invest in digital transformation tools to improve efficiency, reduce costs and speed ‌up time-to-market.",
